# python extension in C
#
1) steps: taking hello, ${input} as an example.

    Step1. create a hello.c
    Step2. create makefile.hello
           make -f makefile.hello
    # or
           create a setup.py
           python setup.py build
           python setup.py install
    Step3. import hello
            print(hello.message('C'))
            print(hello.message('module ' + hello.__file__))

2) an example refer to LearningNotes/python/pythonlet/.

